Note: this file does not claim completeness for all countries listed.

Countries for which data on one or more seasons are missing are given in italics.

In principle only double digit scores from national first divisions are listed, but for several countries more extensive information was added (and indicated as such).

For additional data on high scoring football matches, see also e.g. Séquano-Dionysien.

Finally, for several countries home and away records are not clear for all years. Additions or corrections are welcome.
